content.body: Would it be possible to move our meeting to tomorrow?

content.body: that would work for me, though 1 hour earlier or 1 hour later tomorrow would work even better
i won't be able to make it if it's moved; my days fill up well more than 24 hours in advance :-) no need to schedule on my account alone tho.
